text.text:
Welcome to the cybersecurtiy Forum!
Use the arrow keys or "WASD" keys to walk around. Walk up for an introduction.
You can use shift to run
When you get close to other participants, a white circle will appear and you will be able to videochat (up to four people) - the same as in a real world event.
There are silent areas, where you cannot chat with others (e.g. near doors).
Audience/ Discussion Areas are highlighted: here you can join Group discussions (in the smaller rooms) or listen to the main talks (main stage).
